cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision and deep learning techniques for fisheye image rectification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep neural networks, which suggests that it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of synthesized datasets, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.RO (Robotics).
